channel.title: Newest Technology for a RuneScape Private Server! Must See!
channel.description:
Ok I have been working on this server now since 2003! I have made it completely custome! now you can control ur character with the arrow keys, "a" is to switch between ur spells, "s" is to do various commands such as picking up items, "z" is to activate the selected spell, and "x" is to attack with melee weapons. I am not completely done with it yet, but i think by christmas it should be done. here are some pix. I will be adding more pix and info as soon as i can!
